<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3147000" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="U" oldref="1">Insert Database Columns</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3143284" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="2"><ahelp hid=".uno:SbaBrwInsert"><variable id="datenintext">Inserts all fields of the marked record into the current document at the cursor position.
</variable></ahelp> The icon is only visible if the current document is a text document or a spreadsheet.</paragraph>
<section id="sydatenintext">
<table id="tbl_id3149760">
<tablerow>
